latestPosts.caption:
June’s birthstone, Pearl, it carries a history of poise, intuition, and quiet strength. Found in royal treasuries and sacred rituals, this naturally luminous stone has long symbolised wisdom and clarity.

In Indian tradition, pearls have been treasured not only for their glow but also for their deep connection to balance, calm, and protection.

Join us as Tarang Arora explores the timeless appeal of handcrafted pearl jewellery at Amrapali Jewels — a celebration of grace, legacy, and natural elegance.

#amrapalijewels #junebirthstone #pearllegacy #tarangarora #craftedwithsoul #timelesstreasures #heritagejewelry #jewelsofIndia #modernheirloom #quietluxury

In our latest episode of How Did You Do It?, we sit down with Mr. Tarang Arora, Creative Director & CEO of Amrapali Jewels and Tribe by Amrapali — the brand that redefined Indian heritage jewellery for the modern world.

From being the first Indian jewellery brand at Selfridges to launching a youth-focused sub-brand that’s doubling stores every 1–2 years, this is a story of vision, strategy, and fearless reinvention.

Full episode drops 29th May — subscribe and turn on notifications!

#IndianJeweller #IJMagazine #HowDidYouDoIt #TarangArora #TribeByAmrapali #AmrapaliJewels #JewelleryBusiness #RetailSuccess #IndianJewellery #Entrepreneurship #JewelleryPodcast #BehindTheBrand

Amrapali opens its new flagship store in Juhu, Mumbai — presenting iconic heritage jewellery alongside silver collectibles and curated fashion. A refined space that brings together tradition, design, and culture under one elegant roof.

#amrapalijewels #heritagejewellery #jewellerylaunch #juhumumbai #fineindianjewellery #silvercollectibles #newstorelaunch #elegantspaces #flagshipstore #indianartistry

May’s birthstone, Emerald, is more than just a jewel — it’s a symbol of renewal, wisdom, and timeless beauty. Treasured since ancient civilizations, this vibrant green gem has adorned emperors, queens, and sacred relics across centuries. In Indian heritage, Emeralds have been revered not only for their mesmerizing hue but also for their association with prosperity, intuition, and protection.

Join us as Tarang Arora @tarang_arora explores the enduring magic of handcrafted Emerald jewelry at Amrapali Jewels — celebrating its rich cultural legacy, spiritual symbolism, and eternal allure.

#amrapalijewels #maybirthstone #emerald #tarangarora #emeraldlegacy #jewelsofindia #timelesstreasures #heritagejewelry #craftedwithsoul

latestPosts.caption:
Tarang Arora @tarang_arora walks us through some of Amrapali’s standout creations featuring Aquamarine, the birthstone for March. Known for its tranquil blue hue, aquamarine has long been associated with clarity, courage, and calming energies. Believed to soothe the mind and protect its wearer, this gemstone is beautifully crafted into fine jewelry that speaks of elegance and purpose.

#aquamarine #amrapalijewels #tarangarora #marchbirthstone #gemstonejewelry #birthstonejewelry #calmingenergy #clarityandcourage #indianluxury #heritagejewels #finejewelry #statementpieces #gemstoneguide

I was surprised to find out that today one can start a business in jewellery with much lesser capital that I’d imagined…

Sarthak and Tarang sat down in this episode of Founder’s Office to discuss everything around niches in jewellery where new brands can be built…

How to collaborate with movie stars, stylists, and generate international press…

How to open a store at the airport… and everything else including…

The capital investment, inventory, pricing, capital appreciation of the stock, lab grown diamonds and a lot more…

Promising maximum insights per minute. Always.

And nothing without the Creative Director at Niamh, Aditi Randev.

#casarthakahuja #jewellery #amrapali #aditirandev
